cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI

The paper deals with computer vision and image processing techniques for large-scale 3D urban reconstruction from multi-view aerial images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves deep learning methods, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of a synthetic dataset and the creation of a novel network for depth inference could also be relevant to cs.GR (Graphics) and cs.RO (Robotics).
